# The Origin Story

What started as a simple craving for authentic Thai milk tea turned into a thriving dorm room business. Using traditional techniques and high-quality ingredients imported from Thailand, we crafted a product that delights the Notre Dame community.

# The Journey

## Learning the Craft
- Spent months perfecting the tea brewing process
- Experimented with different tapioca pearl recipes
- Developed a streamlined production system

## Building the Business
- Created a brand identity and menu design
- Set up a pre-order system via Instagram
- Forged a partnership with another student-run startup to provide delivery anywhere on campus

## Growing the Community
- Built a loyal customer base through word-of-mouth
- Hosted boba tasting sessions
- Collaborated with student organizations for events

